Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.59,0:00:12.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悔しい 悔しい 悔しい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.65,0:00:09.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He hates it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.36,0:00:10.93,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He hates it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.93,0:00:12.50,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He hates it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.79,0:00:15.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが これでいい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.92,0:00:15.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But it's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.43,0:00:19.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これでこそ博打
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.47,0:00:17.64,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This is gambling!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.96,0:00:23.76,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji's sleeping instincts catch fire! {clunk}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.00,0:00:22.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジの眠っていた本能に
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.04,0:00:24.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,火がつく
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.59,0:00:30.59,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,{\fad(550,500)\pos(640,505)}Shards of Fate
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.46,0:00:35.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,To an observer, Kaiji's wager must have seemed like a move made of sheer desperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.48,0:00:33.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,端から見れば なかば\Nやけになっているとしか思えない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.35,0:00:35.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジの張り
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.28,0:00:39.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,事実 せきを切ったように\Nカイジは沈んでいく
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.36,0:00:39.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Truly, Kaiji sank beneath a flood of emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.36,0:00:49.95,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But at the same time, something awakened within him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.69,0:00:50.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし同時にカイジの中に\N何かが目覚めていく
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.53,0:00:53.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He risks it all on that awakening!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.83,0:00:52.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その目覚めに賭ける
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.74,0:00:58.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,沈みつつも意地の3000張り
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.75,0:00:58.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Even as he sinks, he clings to a wager of 3,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.78,0:01:04.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,熱く張り続けて40分後
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.80,0:01:04.43,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,40 minutes after he's begun betting in earnest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.43,0:01:06.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji makes another decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.58,0:01:06.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ　再び決断
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.87,0:01:10.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He lays on the Perica--his first bet of 5,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.92,0:01:10.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さらにペリカを重ね\Nバツの5000張り
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.71,0:01:17.30,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And soon, it pays off!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.76,0:01:17.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そしてついに それに呼応する
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.83,0:01:24.95,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,4-5-6! It pays double!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.83,0:01:28.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シゴロ　倍づけ\Nおお！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.65,0:01:29.38,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It appears...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.04,0:01:32.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,表れるカイジの熱が\Nついに宿らしめる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.38,0:01:32.65,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji's spark has caught aflame!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.64,0:01:38.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,サイに幸運を\Nこのひと張りで１万の収入
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.65,0:01:34.73,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Lady Luck smiles on his dice!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.73,0:01:37.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,In one roll, he receives 10,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.98,0:01:41.82,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji, whose stack had shrunken to 28,000, is reborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.25,0:01:41.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２万8000まで落ち込んだカイジ\N復活
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.82,0:01:43.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Back to 38,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.85,0:01:44.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３万8000へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.43,0:01:45.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.59,0:01:48.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして ここで親番
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.67,0:01:47.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Now, he deals!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.12,0:01:50.38,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.19,0:01:52.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,来た　ここだ\Nここで受けずして いつ受ける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.38,0:01:52.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's now or never.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.89,0:01:56.59,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll deal this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.96,0:01:58.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この親を受ける　さあ張ってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.45,0:01:59.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Come on and bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.06,0:02:03.31,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.20,0:02:04.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ\Nしかし
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.75,0:02:09.21,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But the others, sensing Kaiji's aggression, each make small bets!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.54,0:02:06.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジの攻勢を\N見て取ったみんなは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.91,0:02:08.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そろいもそろって小張り
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.81,0:02:14.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負にはいかない　小張りの連続
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.90,0:02:14.32,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A series of pointlessly small bets!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.52,0:02:22.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フフフ… そりゃないよな\Nカイジ君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.51,0:02:22.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's just not your day, huh, Kaiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.12,0:02:25.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,せっかく盛り上がって\N受けた親なのに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.35,0:02:25.26,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You finally decide to deal, and then nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.26,0:02:30.39,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But I understand why they don't want to bet, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.46,0:02:28.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とはいえ ここは\Nいきたくないという
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:30.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,皆の衆の気持ちも分かる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.30,0:02:32.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,困ったな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.39,0:02:31.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.54,0:02:35.53,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh well, I'll take you on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.57,0:02:35.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ま 仕方ない　わしがやるか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.50,0:02:38.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君 初親の景気づけ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.53,0:02:40.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,To celebrate your first deal, I'll make a big bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.24,0:02:41.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,祝儀代わりに大張りを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.79,0:02:43.27,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,20,000 Perica!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.81,0:02:43.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２万ペリカ…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.75,0:02:45.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ俺も
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:45.02,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Me too, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.43,0:02:50.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,These guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.45,0:02:52.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつら　待ってやがったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.24,0:02:54.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Have they been waiting for me to deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.82,0:02:54.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が親を受けるのを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.69,0:02:57.31,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They're trying to wipe me out in one round!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.86,0:02:58.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１発で俺を潰しに来た
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.82,0:02:59.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They each bet 20,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.19,0:03:02.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２人が２万　計４万張り
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.80,0:03:01.83,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Together, that's a bet of 40,000! {And that's bad!}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.33,0:03:04.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I only have 38,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.36,0:03:04.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の手持ちは３万8000
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.75,0:03:07.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If I lose, I can't pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.80,0:03:07.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここで負けたら\Nこの４万は払えない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.46,0:03:10.12,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll have to borrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.64,0:03:10.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,となると当然 借金
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.44,0:03:12.21,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Borrow just to cover it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.44,0:03:12.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かぶせるように借金
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.77,0:03:14.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,借金地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.78,0:03:14.42,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Debt hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.19,0:03:30.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いやいや　こりゃ悪かった
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.79,0:03:30.84,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.84,0:03:34.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd liven things up, but everyone's quieted down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.93,0:03:34.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,盛り上げるつもりが\N少しシーンとさせちまったようだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.80,0:03:37.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし最初に説明したとおり
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.91,0:03:41.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Just as I said from the start, though, 20,000 is this table's maximum wager.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.50,0:03:41.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１人２万は この賭場の正規の上限
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.05,0:03:43.24,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No problem, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.07,0:03:43.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何の問題もない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.10,0:03:46.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,問題が起こるとしたら この後さ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.24,0:03:46.42,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If there's a problem, it'll come after the roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.31,0:03:49.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,サイを振って\Nカイジ君が勝てばいいんだが
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.42,0:03:49.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I hope you win.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.81,0:03:52.71,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Because if you lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.91,0:03:52.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,万が一 負けた時は 事よ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.71,0:03:58.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If my count is correct, you don't have 40,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.81,0:03:56.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしの計算じゃ\N今 カイジ君の手持ちは
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.08,0:04:00.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,４万に届いてない　だろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.54,0:03:59.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.23,0:04:01.26,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.29,0:04:03.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ\Nフフフ　となりゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.56,0:04:08.39,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Then, let me give it to you straight about how things work down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.63,0:04:06.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここは後でモメないように\Nこの地下の取り決めを
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.56,0:04:08.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,伝えておかないとな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.39,0:04:11.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,To put it bluntly, it's about those loans.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.83,0:04:13.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,早い話が借金\N給料前貸しの取り決めだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.10,0:04:13.82,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,How the payday loans work!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.74,0:04:18.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もしカイジ君が負けて\N４万を払うハメになったら
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.82,0:04:18.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If you lose, and have to pay the 40,000...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.04,0:04:22.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしら カイジ君に\N給料の前借りを強要する
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.15,0:04:21.99,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Then you'll be forced to take another advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.99,0:04:23.65,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.21,0:04:26.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でだ ここからが問題なんだが
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:26.12,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The problem is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.08,0:04:30.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すでにカイジ君には\N来月分の給料を前貸し済みだから
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.12,0:04:30.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji, you've already taken an advance on next month's salary.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.59,0:04:36.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今度 貸す金は翌々月分の給料の\N前貸しとなる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.79,0:04:35.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So this will need to come out of your paycheck for the month after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.29,0:04:40.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ま 翌月でもカイジ君が\N重労働に耐え切れず
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.30,0:04:42.93,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Considering the risk of you working yourself to death...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.16,0:04:43.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぶっ倒れるリスクも考え
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.93,0:04:48.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Normally, you receive 60,000 up front...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.10,0:04:48.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,正規の給料の９万ではなく\N６万を払っているんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.34,0:04:54.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But for two months in advance, I'll need a larger cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.40,0:04:51.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,翌々月となれば\N必然的に こちらとしては
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.94,0:04:55.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さらに払うわけにはいかなくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.54,0:05:00.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言いにくいんだが\Nここは心を鬼にして伝えないとな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.56,0:05:00.27,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It hurts to say this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:04.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,For two months in advance, you'll get half your check.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.38,0:05:04.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,翌々月分の前貸しは\N正規の９万の半分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.79,0:05:07.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji's advance will be 45,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.79,0:05:07.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジへの前貸し ４万5000
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:12.38,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Everyone here's okay with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.99,0:05:12.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そういうことで ここの皆の衆には\N納得してもらってる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.38,0:05:14.89,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't blame me, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.39,0:05:16.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪く思わんでくれ フフフ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.77,0:05:20.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フッ なるほど
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.39,0:05:19.88,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.60,0:05:23.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こりゃ見損なってたぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.64,0:05:22.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.72,0:05:25.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're a total dick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.07,0:05:25.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大した悪党じゃないか あんた
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:29.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,60,000? 45,000? Are you shitting me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.97,0:05:29.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よく言うぜ\N何が６万 ４万5000だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.60,0:05:34.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're like an antlion, setting up his muddy pit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.84,0:05:34.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝手にアリ地獄\N泥沼みたいな制度を作っといて
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.07,0:05:36.86,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Everyone here's okay with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.12,0:05:36.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢皆の衆には\N納得してもらってる｣だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.86,0:05:38.17,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.89,0:05:40.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカ野郎　その前借り生活から\N抜けるには
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.17,0:05:43.39,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,To get out of that hole, someone needs to go two whole months without food!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.62,0:05:43.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２ヵ月を無休で乗り切らなきゃ\Nならないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.39,0:05:46.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが 一度飲み食いを覚えたら\Nもう不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.39,0:05:46.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But the memory alone makes it impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.76,0:05:49.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,理不尽と思っても\N毎月 給料日になると
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.78,0:05:51.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But on payday, unreasonable as it may be, you'll take it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.63,0:05:52.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たぶん受け取っちまう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.07,0:05:55.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして ずっとずっと\N受け取り続ける
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.13,0:05:58.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And you just keep taking that 45,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.57,0:05:58.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,目減りした４万5000をな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.17,0:06:02.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クッ これは体のいい\Nピンハネじゃねえか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.94,0:06:01.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's nothing but a kickback to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:04.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今にして思えば\Nあのちんけなビールの
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.05,0:06:06.86,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That shitty beer and junk food is the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.95,0:06:07.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,差し入れからしてそうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.28,0:06:10.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まず狙った標的の欲望を刺激し
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:10.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You work someone's hunger up...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.49,0:06:16.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,金を使わせ 最終的には\Nこのギャンブルに巻き込む
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.51,0:06:12.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Get them to spend their money...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.07,0:06:15.39,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Then drag them into this game!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.29,0:06:19.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いるんだよな そんな人間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.38,0:06:19.33,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I didn't think anyone could be that terrible of a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.85,0:06:24.57,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You work alongside us down here... You share our fate...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.93,0:06:24.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな地下で共に働く\N同じように追い詰められた仲間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.57,0:06:29.09,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You steal our pennies and drain us of our blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:29.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな仲間の細い金に取りつく\N生き血をすする
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.09,0:06:31.45,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're a leech!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.14,0:06:31.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヒルみたいな人間がよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.07,0:06:39.18,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Aw man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.15,0:06:39.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,参ったな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:42.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんなの便宜を考えてやった\Nサービスだが
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.18,0:06:45.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I try to make everyone's life a little happier, and this is the thanks I get?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.45,0:06:45.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな見当違いの非難を\N浴びてしまうとは
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.34,0:06:51.26,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji. I'm your boss. Your business is my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.75,0:06:51.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君　いくらみんなの世話を\N焼くのが務めの班長とはいえ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.13,0:06:54.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしだって\Nただで尽くすわけにはいかんさ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.26,0:06:54.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I can't just back off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.46,0:06:58.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いくばくかの見返りは\Nもらわんと　だろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.66,0:06:58.38,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So I need a little something in exchange, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.70,0:07:03.97,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Now, go ahead and roll. We can't get started until the dealer rolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.77,0:07:03.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ振ってくれ　親のカイジ君が\N振らないと勝負は始まらない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.97,0:07:08.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And hey, if you win, there's no problem at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.97,0:07:08.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なあに　カイジ君が勝てば\N何の問題もない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.97,0:07:18.12,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You all knew, didn't you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.02,0:07:19.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,知ってたんだろ？あんたら\Nえっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.62,0:07:23.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That we were playing tonight to break me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.65,0:07:23.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この賭場は\N俺を落とす賭場だってことを
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.59,0:07:26.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,隣の新入り三好は ともかく
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.67,0:07:28.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't know about Miyoshi here, but the rest of you all knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.16,0:07:28.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,他の連中は みんな知っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.44,0:07:30.82,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You knew, and you said nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.53,0:07:30.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,知っていて黙っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.82,0:07:32.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Not a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.90,0:07:34.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何のことはない\Nみんな消極的とはいえ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.36,0:07:37.25,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're all so set in your ways that you support him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.57,0:07:37.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この班長に協力してたってわけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.25,0:07:41.88,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Even as you grumble about his control.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.31,0:07:42.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほんとは班長の強権に\N不満 不平を抱いてるくせによ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.15,0:07:46.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're afraid of his glare, and you go along.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.21,0:07:47.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのくせ睨まれるのが怖くて\N仕方なく協力する
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.95,0:07:50.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな奴らは大嫌いだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.01,0:07:50.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I hate people like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.85,0:07:52.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,班長も許せねえが
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.85,0:07:56.95,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I won't forgive him, but I won't forgive slimy bastards like you, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.89,0:07:58.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そういうどっちつかずの\Nぬらぬらした奴らも許せねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.79,0:07:59.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Who are you expecting to lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.13,0:08:00.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰が負けるか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.96,0:08:02.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は勝つ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.03,0:08:02.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll win!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.43,0:08:11.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll win, right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.57,0:08:12.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここで ここで勝つ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.14,0:08:14.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負けるわけにはいかない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.23,0:08:14.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I can't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.60,0:08:18.04,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Win or lose... There is no other way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.61,0:08:18.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,天地　勝つと負けるじゃ天地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.04,0:08:23.17,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If I lose, I'll sink deeper and deeper into the abyss!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.11,0:08:23.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負ければ この地下の底の底で\Nさらに搾り取られる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.62,0:08:27.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,With half my pay forfeited, I'll be nothing more than a slave!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.65,0:08:27.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,給料の半分もピンハネされて\Nまさに奴隷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.69,0:08:31.14,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll sink! Sink to the bottom!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.86,0:08:32.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,沈む　このまま沈んじまう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.44,0:08:34.20,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But if I win...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.46,0:08:35.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし勝てば 勝てば４万
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.20,0:08:38.62,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's 40,000! I'll have 78,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.73,0:08:39.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手持ちの合計は７万8000になる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.94,0:08:42.82,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I can pay back the 60,000 I borrowed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.00,0:08:42.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,となれば借りた６万を\N班長に叩き返しても
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.82,0:08:44.84,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And have 18,000 left!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.87,0:08:45.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ１万8000残る
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.34,0:08:47.71,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I can start over! I can see!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.37,0:08:48.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やり直せる　目指せる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.11,0:08:51.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの１日外出券を
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:50.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The hope of the one-day furlough...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.40,0:08:53.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,rests on one roll of the dice!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.41,0:08:53.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,サイの目１つで
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.43,0:08:59.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:09:03.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クソ クソ クソ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.10,0:09:02.21,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,God damnit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.89,0:09:05.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Why do I always end up like this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.06,0:09:06.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんでいつもこうなるんだ 俺は
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.39,0:09:11.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつもそんな役割ばかり\Nこんな地下地獄に落ちたのは
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.42,0:09:08.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,These tasks...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.85,0:09:14.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm only down here because I cosigned a loan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.03,0:09:14.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,元はといえば保証人を頼まれて\N断り切れなかったからだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.90,0:09:15.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.90,0:09:17.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが 落ちたら落ちたで
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.85,0:09:20.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Even down here, they're after me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.44,0:09:20.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな奴らに標的にされる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.08,0:09:21.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.21,0:09:22.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クソ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.95,0:09:29.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,目は５\Nおお！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.05,0:09:29.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He rolls a five!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.95,0:09:35.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よし　まずまず\Nそうさ　今 俺は上り調子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.97,0:09:32.40,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All right! That's a start!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.40,0:09:35.38,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Things are looking up for me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.38,0:09:37.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Nothing's gone wrong yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.46,0:09:40.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,下手な目は まず出ないはずなんだ\N当然だ この結果は
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.78,0:09:39.59,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Of course I'd roll something good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.89,0:09:43.89,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Looks like you've dug your own grave, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.16,0:09:44.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,潰すつもりが\Nとんだ墓穴を掘ったな 班長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.89,0:09:49.53,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes! In chinchirorin, a five is a good, strong roll!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:49.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう　チンチロにおける５の目は\N相当強い いい目である
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.53,0:09:54.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The odds of any roll but triples or 4-5-6 is the same,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.54,0:09:52.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,目の出る確率は\Nぞろ目 シゴロを除けば
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.54,0:09:56.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どの数字でも同じ108分の15
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.34,0:09:56.25,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,15 out of 108!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.08,0:09:58.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが５に勝つのは６しかない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.25,0:09:58.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But only a six can defeat a five!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.91,0:10:02.28,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The odds of a one through four are four out of six!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.98,0:10:01.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１から４が出る確率は６の４倍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.95,0:10:05.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,目なしを入れれば\Nその確率はもっと高くなる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.28,0:10:05.86,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Add in busts, and the odds are even better!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.75,0:10:09.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,５は９割近く\N負けを知らぬ目と言っていい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.86,0:10:09.62,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A five stands merely a ten percent chance of losing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.46,0:10:13.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Aww jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.56,0:10:13.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっちゃー
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.53,0:10:17.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,事実 三好以下は\N軒並みカイジの５に屈し
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.63,0:10:18.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Indeed, one by one, beginning with Miyoshi, the players lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.37,0:10:19.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３連敗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.30,0:10:22.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして いよいよ２万張りの１人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.44,0:10:24.99,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And then the bowl passes to the first bet of 20,000, the boss's lackey, Isawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.07,0:10:25.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,班長側の石和にどんぶりが回る
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.43,0:10:29.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No other roll matters to Kaiji now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.51,0:10:29.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジにとって今\N他の張りなど どうでもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.36,0:10:33.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The only things that matter are the rolls of this man and the boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.38,0:10:33.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,問題は班長大槻と この男の振り
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.45,0:10:39.39,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Isawa makes his fateful first roll!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.45,0:10:39.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,石和 注目の第１投
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.26,0:10:45.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,目は４\Nよし
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.32,0:10:43.62,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He rolls a four!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.62,0:10:44.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:47.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よしよし まずは１勝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.49,0:10:48.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's it! It starts with a victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.70,0:10:52.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうぞ\Nうん
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.72,0:10:50.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.88,0:10:54.88,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Next, the boss, Ohtsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.30,0:10:54.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,続いて班長大槻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.24,0:10:59.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出るな　出てたまるか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.33,0:11:00.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He won't get it! He can't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.31,0:11:04.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,５以上の目など
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.34,0:11:03.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Nothing over five!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.48,0:11:13.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,再び４　班長側２連敗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.50,0:11:11.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Another four!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.07,0:11:13.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The boss's side fails twice!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.15,0:11:17.11,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I... I... I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.29,0:11:17.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,や… や… やった！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.11,0:11:19.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I did it I did it I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.16,0:11:19.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やった やった やった
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.09,0:11:23.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん\Nよし 生き残った　生き残ったぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.34,0:11:20.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.46,0:11:23.62,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All right! I'm still alive! I'm still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.62,0:11:25.12,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.93,0:11:27.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の勝ち　復活だ 復活
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.12,0:11:27.71,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm back! I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.47,0:11:34.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ついに はい上がった\N借金漬けのピンハネ地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.51,0:11:34.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji rises from the hell of debt!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:36.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これで また目指せる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.44,0:11:36.32,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,His eyes reopen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.88,0:11:40.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの１日外出券を
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.91,0:11:40.39,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,To the one-day furlough!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:47.41,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.99,0:11:48.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,失礼します
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.89,0:11:52.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,珍しいよな\N班長が大勝負に負けるの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.98,0:11:52.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Huh, the boss doesn't normally lose when it's on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.13,0:11:58.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結局 沼川を含め班長側は３連敗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.15,0:11:58.26,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,In the end, counting Numakawa, the boss's side loses three in a row!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.03,0:12:02.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その後の子も ことごとく\Nカイジの５を上回れず
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.26,0:12:02.40,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,None of the remaining players can beat Kaiji's five, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.40,0:12:05.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji wins every match as dealer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.54,0:12:05.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ　この親 全勝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.01,0:12:07.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うひょー！ハハハ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.74,0:12:11.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪いな みんな　悪いな\Nでは遠慮なく
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.83,0:12:12.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that, guys! I'll be taking all of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.48,0:12:17.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい\Nはい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.52,0:12:16.42,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.59,0:12:20.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.85,0:12:21.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうぞ\Nうん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.84,0:12:38.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,へっ サイひと振りで\N４万2200の収入
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.78,0:12:38.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,42,200 with a single roll of the dice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.52,0:12:42.04,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I was losing all night, but now I've turned it around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.57,0:12:42.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負けが込んでいた勝負が\Nひと振りで一気に逆転
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.04,0:12:43.57,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm ahead of the game now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.04,0:12:43.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,プラスに持っていった
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.98,0:12:47.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,８万あれば\N例の前借り６万を返しても
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.15,0:12:49.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,With 80,000 I can pay him back and still have twenty thou left.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.85,0:12:50.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ２万残る
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.22,0:12:55.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,班長が いくら俺を潰そうとしても\N親さえしのげばいい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.50,0:12:54.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All I need to do to get out from under him is survive my turn as dealer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.50,0:13:00.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The players choose their bets, so I can keep my hands to sixty thou easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.96,0:13:00.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,子は張りをｺﾝﾄﾛｰﾙできるから\N前借りの６万を残して生き残れる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:05.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君　親は２回
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.89,0:13:05.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji. Dealers go twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.43,0:13:07.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,え？\Nみんな そうしてきたろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.12,0:13:08.04,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We've all been doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.94,0:13:12.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１回で終わるのは目なしや\Nピンの目 ヒフミが出た時だけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.04,0:13:12.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You only get to quit at one if you roll a one, a bust, or a 1-2-3.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.74,0:13:16.02,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't go passing the bowl off yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.77,0:13:16.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とぼけて回すなよ どんぶりを
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.34,0:13:19.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ… ああ そうか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.34,0:13:19.03,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.03,0:13:22.03,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Sorry, guys. I wasn't paying attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.25,0:13:22.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪い悪い　ついうっかりしてたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.03,0:13:25.17,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I wasn't trying to trick you or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.08,0:13:25.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや マジで\Nごまかす気なんてねえさ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.02,0:13:28.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ張ってくれ\N今なら負ける気がしねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.17,0:13:28.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All right, make your bets and make sure you're cool with losing them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.54,0:13:31.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,History's gonna repeat itself! {puuuuush}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.76,0:13:33.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１回も２回も同じことさ\Nさあ張ってくれ　え？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.46,0:13:32.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So, go ahead and bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.50,0:13:40.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,班長たち　再び２万ずつ４万張り
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.57,0:13:40.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The boss and his lackey each bet 20,000, for a total of 40,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.55,0:13:44.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Seriously? You're seriously still trying to take me down?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.94,0:13:44.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,マジかよ　あくまで\N潰しに来るってか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.55,0:13:48.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, we're not after anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.81,0:13:48.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いやいや 潰すとか何とか\Nそんなんじゃないさ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.96,0:13:52.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We just feel like the dice are cooling off for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.98,0:13:52.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ単純に そろそろ\N目の下がる頃かと思ってさ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.78,0:13:56.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,けっ 何を言ってやがる\N細い目ギラギラさせやがって
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.46,0:13:55.02,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.02,0:13:59.38,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're sitting back there all shifty-eyed! Of course you're trying to break me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.98,0:14:00.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,満々じゃねえか 潰す気で\Nフフフ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.69,0:14:04.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,けど悪いが見誤ってるぜ\Nその押し
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.70,0:14:04.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but you're reading us wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:06.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're throwing your money away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.43,0:14:09.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,捨て金だ それは\Nまだ俺には目が出るはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:08.83,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The dice are still gonna come up for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.06,0:14:11.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フフフ　わしはないと見た
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.06,0:14:12.28,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Doesn't look that way to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.97,0:14:14.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はっ さっさと張れ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.23,0:14:14.77,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.94,0:14:17.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,間を空けさせるな\Nはい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.13,0:14:16.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't slow things down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.69,0:14:17.62,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.28,0:14:27.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今なら出る 出る 今なら
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.40,0:14:25.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They'll come up! I know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.96,0:14:27.09,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.62,0:14:33.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 振れば出る
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.62,0:14:33.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If I roll, they'll come up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.65,0:14:37.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 振れば強い目が出る
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.66,0:14:34.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If I roll now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.85,0:14:36.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll roll well!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.85,0:14:38.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Here goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.96,0:14:39.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いくぜ\Nはい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.91,0:14:39.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.69,0:14:55.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji rolls again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.74,0:14:57.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ　２度振って２度目なし
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.66,0:14:57.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And again, a bust!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.61,0:15:02.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フフフ　な？そろそろ引き潮だろ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.94,0:15:01.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Well? Shall I take my money now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.03,0:15:03.24,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.12,0:15:05.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クソ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.07,0:15:10.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The three dice can come up 216 different ways!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.09,0:15:08.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３個のサイコロの\N目の組み合わせは
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.29,0:15:11.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全部で216通り
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.94,0:15:16.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Of those, including 1-2-3, there are 108 valid rolls in chinchirorin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.03,0:15:13.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのうちヒフミを含め108を
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.93,0:15:16.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チンチロは目と定めている
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.46,0:15:21.24,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So the odds of a successful roll are just fifty percent! {exactly also implied}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.56,0:15:21.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり１回振って目の出る確率は\Nジャスト50パーセント
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.24,0:15:26.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,With three rolls, the odds climb to 87.5%!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.34,0:15:24.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３回振れば確率は ぐっと上がって
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.14,0:15:26.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,87.5パーセント
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.66,0:15:30.12,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Roll three times, and something will come up nearly 90% of the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.67,0:15:31.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり３回振れば\N９割近く目が出る
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:33.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頼む　出ろ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.46,0:15:34.14,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Please! Come up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.06,0:15:38.62,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The crucial third roll!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.08,0:15:38.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,明暗分かつ３投目
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.65,0:15:50.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Look! A six! I rolled a six!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.70,0:15:50.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見ろ　６だ！６だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.46,0:15:54.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の勝ちだ　やった！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.67,0:15:52.21,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.21,0:15:53.64,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.44,0:15:59.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,救われた　ギリギリの最後で
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.46,0:15:58.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm saved! That was a close call!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.64,0:16:01.99,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Saved by that one last bit of luck...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.07,0:16:02.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,強運の流れ　欠片に
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.81,0:16:04.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やった やった やった
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.90,0:16:04.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All riiiiiight!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.75,0:16:07.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はしゃぐなよ\Nえ？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:06.22,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't get too excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.52,0:16:10.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ確定したわけじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.58,0:16:09.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This isn't over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.38,0:16:14.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一部　残っている\Nこっちの勝ち目も
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.49,0:16:13.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I have one chance left to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.91,0:16:15.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.02,0:16:16.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝ち目？\Nそうさ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.19,0:16:19.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah. In normal chinchiro, your six would end things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.62,0:16:19.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,通常のチンチロなら\Nこの６で終わり
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.66,0:16:21.65,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The dealer would take all the bets.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.86,0:16:24.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,親の総取りさ\N子はサイを振ることはできない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.65,0:16:24.37,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The players wouldn't even get to roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.37,0:16:26.73,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But here, we roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.43,0:16:26.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが ここじゃ振れるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.73,0:16:30.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,振れる以上 どんな小さい確率でも
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.73,0:16:32.18,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We roll, and no matter how small the chance is, it's still a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.17,0:16:32.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,可能性は残されている
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.18,0:16:36.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If we roll a six like you, it's a draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.21,0:16:36.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君の出目と同じ６を出せば\N引き分けだし
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.46,0:16:39.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And if we roll a 4-5-6 or triples, the tables are turned.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:39.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もしシゴロやゾロ目を\N出したら逆転
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.45,0:16:42.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,逆にこっちの勝ちってわけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:42.38,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Then, we win.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.32,0:16:46.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だろ？まだ望みは残っている
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.38,0:16:43.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.19,0:16:46.26,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A hope still remains.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.90,0:16:53.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Really? Is he serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.06,0:16:52.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,マジ？マジに\N本気で言ってるわけ？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.96,0:16:57.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本気さ　だって事実そうだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.10,0:16:54.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Dead serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.70,0:16:56.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm right, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.16,0:17:01.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,へっ バカ　起きねえんだよ\Nそんなことは
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.26,0:16:58.89,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.89,0:17:01.21,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,There's no way that'll happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.21,0:17:05.33,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Sure, if you roll long enough, you'll eventually get triples or a 4-5-6.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.44,0:17:05.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そりゃ たくさん握って振りゃ\Nシゴロもゾロ目も出るさ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.14,0:17:07.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが今まさにここ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.33,0:17:09.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But no way in hell are you getting 'em right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.07,0:17:10.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この瞬間になんて\N出たりゃしねえっての
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:13.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're not gonna get that lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.28,0:17:13.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなに都合よくいくわけ\Nねえじゃねえか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.16,0:17:16.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Even you should be smart enough to figure that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.18,0:17:16.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かってんだろ？んなこと\Nあんただって
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.47,0:17:18.88,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You should know that damn well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.62,0:17:18.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,腐るほど味わってきたはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.45,0:17:23.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Sure, Kaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.49,0:17:25.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かるよ カイジ君\Nカイジ君の言うことも
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.34,0:17:25.50,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.36,0:17:29.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし それでも何というか\Nわしは信じていてのお
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.50,0:17:29.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But, I still believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.86,0:17:34.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,念が時に\Nサイの目を左右することを
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.94,0:17:34.24,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Sometimes raw will weighs on the dice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.24,0:17:35.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.24,0:17:37.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,は？\N念力が高めるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.34,0:17:39.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,When someone's will is unleashed, it can even bring them back from the dead. {clunk}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.20,0:17:39.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,起死回生の可能性を
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.61,0:17:42.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ね… 念力だと？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:41.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Willpower!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.98,0:17:43.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You understand, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.01,0:17:43.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.94,0:17:47.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かるかよ んなこと　アハハ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.39,0:17:47.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,How the hell am I supposed to understand that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.82,0:17:51.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんましバカバカしくて\Nついていけねえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.94,0:17:51.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's too retarded for me to follow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.05,0:17:53.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハハハ　マジ念力かよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.99,0:17:53.68,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Willpower? Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.59,0:17:57.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そりゃすげえよ　最高だぜ あんた
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.68,0:17:55.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're killing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.51,0:17:57.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're just perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.46,0:17:59.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アハハ　念力？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.26,0:18:00.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Willpower...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.93,0:18:03.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確かにバカげている　しかし
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.13,0:18:01.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He does look like a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.87,0:18:03.27,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.27,0:18:08.02,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But! The boss's lackey Isawa makes his roll!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.36,0:18:07.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし班長側の石和の１投目
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.11,0:18:13.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シゴロ　倍づけ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.23,0:18:13.03,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A 4-5-6! It pays double!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.03,0:18:14.97,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.04,0:18:15.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おっしゃー！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.75,0:18:20.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヘヘ　２万の倍づけは４万
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.56,0:18:20.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Double on a 20 thousamd bet is 40 thou.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.65,0:18:23.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これでお前の\Nさっきの勝ちは飛んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.80,0:18:23.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's your win before, right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.65,0:18:27.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手持ち８万は\Nあっという間に残り４万
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.72,0:18:26.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,From 80 thousand right back down to 40.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.15,0:18:29.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バ… バカな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.83,0:18:29.17,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.72,0:18:31.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんでこんなことが…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.84,0:18:31.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Why is this happening!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.67,0:18:34.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And the boss, Ohtsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.76,0:18:34.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして班長大槻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.00,0:18:45.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カツ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.14,0:18:55.24,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Im-Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.18,0:18:55.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まさか… まさか…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.33,0:19:16.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君　博打は恐ろしいな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.38,0:19:16.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Gambling is a frightening thing, isn't it, Kaiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.69,0:19:19.20,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Really, truly frightening.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.74,0:19:18.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほんとに博打は恐ろしい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.93,0:19:24.45,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The boss Ohtsuki rolls three fives!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.04,0:19:24.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,班長大槻　なんと５ゾロ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.35,0:19:26.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３倍づけ　圧勝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.45,0:19:27.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It pays triple! A total victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.95,0:19:29.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そ… そんなバカな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.10,0:19:29.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.19,0:19:31.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,How did this happen!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.38,0:19:32.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんでこんな目が\Nこんなバカなことが…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.13,0:19:32.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This makes no sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.46,0:19:42.20,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Kaiji, but you're bankrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.49,0:19:42.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君　悪いが\Nこれであんたは破産だ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.20,0:19:46.25,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Triples pay triple, so you owe me 60,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.36,0:19:46.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,５ゾロは３倍づけだから\N２万張りは６万払い
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.25,0:19:51.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You only have 40,000. You can't pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.30,0:19:51.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君の手持ち４万では\Nこの６万は補えない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.35,0:19:53.21,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're short...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.41,0:19:55.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんたマイナス２万！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.21,0:19:55.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Twenty thousand!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.98,0:20:00.24,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji! Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.05,0:20:00.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん！カイジさん！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.55,0:20:03.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして　なんで？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.63,0:20:03.23,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Why? Why!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.08,0:20:06.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな こんな\Nこんな理不尽なことが
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.23,0:20:09.26,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Why does this bullshit always happen to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.95,0:20:10.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺のみばかりに…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.29,0:20:15.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ 卒倒　地の底の底の底でも
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.33,0:20:12.65,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji passes out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.65,0:20:18.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,In the depths of the abyss, he enters debt hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.06,0:20:18.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,借金地獄突入
